      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Start Your Preparedness Journey</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600 mb-8">Choose a category to explore essential guides and gear recommendations.</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
